| Change | Saves per theme | Risks | Worth it? |
|---|---|---|---|
| Auto-derive palette dark* | 12 lines → 0 lines of getters | Lose hue/chroma tuning from classic themes | ✅ **Yes** — with `overrides` escape hatch |
| Extract spread constants | 0 lines saved | None — pure documentation | ✅ **Yes** — makes intent visible |
| `primaryScale` builder | -1 line (net neutral) | Hides spread values behind config | ❔ **Discuss** — marginal win at best |

